要用 PHP 連接 MySQL database 嘅時候，可以試下以下呢段簡單嘅程式碼，教你點樣安全咁處理用戶輸入嘅資料：

```php
<?php
$servername = "localhost";
$username = "safe_user";
$password = "SecurePass123!";
$dbname = "app_data";

// Create connection
$conn = new mysqli($servername, $username, $password, $dbname);

// Check connection
if ($conn->connect_error) {
    error_log("Connection failed: " . $conn->connect_error);
    die("系統暫時有問題，請稍後再試。");
}

// Example of safely handling user input
$user_input = $_GET['search'] ?? '';
$stmt = $conn->prepare("SELECT * FROM products WHERE name LIKE ?");
$search_term = "%" . $user_input . "%";
$stmt->bind_param("s", $search_term);
$stmt->execute();
$result = $stmt->get_result();

// Close connection
$conn->close();
?>
```

呢段 code 主要係示範點樣安全咁處理用戶輸入，避免 SQL injection 嘅風險。記得喺實際應用時，要用啱啲安全措施，例如 prepared statements 同埋驗證用戶輸入嘅資料。

